metadata.name: Moody Motel Room
metadata.description:
Self Love #2

A moody motel room in Black & White.

She gets to ease into the night and as it unfolds she letâ€™s go of the day she had.

A mind, that enjoys the serenity and peace it brings.

What a delight to enjoy some peace of mind. We go through every day, without taking a moment for ourselves, and I need it, we need it.

Let go. Let it out. Let it be what it may. Make healthy habits become a thing, I deserve it and so do you.

Take care of your mind, your body and your soul.
Let it rest and be free.

This is a reminder to all females out there, cultivate habits of self love, you deserve it.

- Shot on Pentax KX
- Ilford HP5 Plus - 35mm
- Shenzhen, China, 2022
